    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Candlestick designed for use on the Epiphany on January 6, intended to hold three candles. A common design includes a central spike to hold a wax candle with two flanking cups to hold tallow candles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
